{"tid":2117610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民陣聲援戴耀廷 撐初選合法","createTime":"2020-07-21T03:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T03:26:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"08471d5ffeb56eed7da60aa8f51144403451263b","tid":2117610,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T03:26:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200721/S6722YJTIUR6IORNA34UODG2EE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FS6722YJTIUR6IORNA34UODG2EE%2F&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=cb4e030d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FS6722YJTIUR6IORNA34UODG2EE%2F&h=93c07f02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200721/S6722YJTIUR6IORNA34UODG2EE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民陣聲援戴耀廷 撐初選合法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bTKG8_VM6WaWFXNxoOn1EYV7bQU=/947x768/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E45IDB3VRFGXC4O33FP7JMEIRI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbTKG8_VM6WaWFXNxoOn1EYV7bQU%3D%2F947x768%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE45IDB3VRFGXC4O33FP7JMEIRI.gif&h=dca5347b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民陣昨開記招，多位初選參選者到場聲援戴耀廷。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。多個初選參選者昨出席民陣記者會，以「35+抗爭 不屈不撓」、「迎戰DQ 再接再厲」、「反對DQ 齊上齊落」為口號，聲援戴耀廷等多個初選籌辦者，又呼籲港人9.6選舉日投票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰：佢係票王<br />\n<br />\n早前兩名初選組織者。。。。。。。。。。。。。民陣副召集人陳皓桓昨於記者會上力撐戴耀廷，指民主派初選合法、合理、合憲，並不違反港版國安法，否則應仔細說明「邊個位犯咗乜嘢法」，港澳辦、中聯辦及特區政府應尊重選民選擇，也要尊重民主派參選權，不要DQ任何人，否則將視為DQ整個民主派。<br />\n<br />\n已遞表參選九東的黃之鋒表示，過去一星期初選籌辦者都受到兩辦打。。。。。。。。。。。，指整個民主陣營都受打壓，民主派將聯成一線對抗暴政，「我哋要幫冇得發聲嘅出聲」。<br />\n<br />\n社民連岑子杰感謝61萬港人無懼打壓堅持投票，強調民主派會團結一致對抗專制政權，又言戴耀廷才是初選的「票王」，。。。。。。。。。。。"}]}